Husband | Father | Musician | Video Editor | Sound Designer | Voice Actor | Actor | Gif Creator

He was former front man for the band Dust alongside Jamie Murphy and Franny Griffiths from the Liverpool band Space who had hits like Female of The Species, Tom Jones & Neighborhood with Vinnie Jamison, drummer for Echo & The Bunnymen.

Vinnie Camilleri now writes as a solo artist creating music of many varied styles. Vinnie's current project is creating Dark Nordic Folk Viking music which played daily on DANNHEIM 's radio station the creator of music from the epic TV series Vikings.
